# 🛰️ Sextant Orbital Resilience Framework  
## v1.1 Architecture Layer — Unified Runtime Specification

## 🧭 Overview
v1.1 introduces a modular orchestration architecture that separates simulation, prediction, and governance into structured execution layers while maintaining deterministic system behavior.

This version evolves the framework from a standalone simulation engine into a coordinated unified runtime system.

---

## 🧱 Core Architecture Stack (v1.1)

### 1. Core Layer (Deterministic Engine)
- SimulationEngine
- deterministic step execution
- scenario loading
- event trace logging

### 2. Cascade Layer
- OrbitalCascadeModel
- failure propagation
- dependency impact tracking

### 3. Predictive Layer
- PredictiveCascadeEngine
- risk scoring
- critical node detection

### 4. Orchestration Layer (NEW)
- SystemFlowController
- coordinates cascade + prediction + governance
- produces unified runtime audit

### 5. Unified Runtime Layer (NEW)
- UnifiedRuntime
- single system entrypoint
- aggregates execution outputs

### 6. Scenario Layer
- ScenarioEngine
- event sequencing
- time-based cascade simulation

### 7. Observability Layer
- MissionDashboard
- system state visualization
- cascade and timeline inspection

### 8. Runtime Context Layer
- shared system state container
- cross-module synchronization

### 9. Concept Layers (Non-Executable)

#### 🕶 Stealth Mode
- controlled observability abstraction
- reduced logging / filtered outputs

#### ⚛ Quantum Transition Model
- conceptual scenario branching model
- multi-path system evolution

---

## 🔗 Execution Flow

Scenario Input  
→ SimulationEngine  
→ CascadeModel  
→ PredictiveEngine  
→ SystemFlowController  
→ UnifiedRuntime  
→ MissionDashboard  

